Package com.c2g4.SingHealthWebApp.Admin.Report

Class ReportBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.c2g4.SingHealthWebApp.Admin.Report.ReportBuilder
public class ReportBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
ReportBuilder serves as a builder for the ReportObject as well as provides utility functions for the handling of ReportObjects.
